{"tid":2499120,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"江西公安副廳長落馬 家中被搜出AK47步槍、兩億人民幣 、810萬美元、6公斤黃金","createTime":"2021-04-21T15:42:43.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-21T15:53:10.000Z","uid":222970,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"07adb5e5fbbb2da0dfad8ab1336e580a0be6a548","tid":2499120,"uid":222970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:42:43.000Z","msg":"江西政法高官落馬 傳抄出2億元和AK47衝鋒鎗<br />\n北京時間：2021-04-20 08:38<br />\n<br />\n【新唐人北京時間2021年04月20日訊】曾任中共江西省公安廳常務副廳長的葉國兵，近日被通報正在接受監察機構的調查。有原中共體制內人士爆料，葉國兵被抓時，辦案人員從他兒子家中搜出人民幣逾兩億、美元數百萬、黃金逾6公斤，還搜出AK47衝鋒鎗、手槍等一批槍支彈藥。<br />\n<br />\n中共江西省紀委監委4月16日發布通告稱，現任江西省政協社會和法制委員會副主任葉國兵「涉嫌嚴重違紀違法」，正接受省紀委監委的「紀律審查」和「監察調查」。<br />\n<br />\n據公開資訊，葉國兵是原中共江西省委統戰部部長葉學齡的兒子，現年60歲，江西進賢人，長期在中共公安系統工作，職務一路晉升， 2019年8月至2000年12月曾擔任江西省公安廳黨委副書記、常務副廳長，其後退居二線任現職。<br />\n<br />\n週一（19日），旅居日本的原中共體制內人士許梅邨在推特發帖稱，有來自中國南昌的消息指，葉國兵今年4月13日凌晨兩點左右被抓時，他的妻子、兒子及兒媳也同時被「隔離審查」。辦案人員從葉國兵兒子的家裏搜到了<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\"><strong>2億多元人民幣、810萬元美金、3.02萬元港幣、6.2公斤黃金，以及Ak47衝鋒鎗和64式手槍各一把，子彈900多發</strong></span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n上述消息被眾多華人網友在推特上轉發，並引來熱議。多數網友都針對葉國兵兒子家中搜出的槍支彈藥進行調侃和譏諷。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/Qmb9UJNJbLr8cAwKhnyAcK3kJhzun5Cv5ncoDweubFoDMC?filename=Q9vxXJE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ9vxXJE.jpg&h=60c26dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmR1sxs6PovnXSkttwUnJm8DT1imza2uH2EpDeByBG7Y7v?filename=g3JC8Qk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3JC8Qk.jpg&h=006f1bbb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2021/04/19/a103099634.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com%2Fb5%2F2021%2F04%2F19%2Fa103099634.html&d=tbI6yIPhVaIexgVZB5ClnQp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=63820c84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ntdtv.com/b5/2021/04/19/a103099634.html</a>"},{"pid":"fcf71a35d7a3e9a41e5b5c4288c895b3400a6e40","tid":2499120,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:44:13.000Z","msg":"3.02萬元港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該係買嘢用剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd5fcc2c2554bd6069a4ff3ce8a4e5cfa4df75d9","tid":2499120,"uid":1781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:45:29.000Z","msg":"為黨工作這樣也能是貪污嗎"},{"pid":"b53800db4710ddab1d8a3b227c4fd1b093a1e18e","tid":2499120,"uid":25240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcf71a35d7a3e9a41e5b5c4288c895b3400a6e40","tid":2499120,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:44:13.000Z","msg":"3.02萬元港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該係買嘢用剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:49:08.000Z","msg":"個江西公安廳廳長係副部級<br />\n咁呢個副廳長低一級姐係正廳級左右<br />\n<br />\n正廳級都貪到咁多<br />\n再上去真係不敢想像<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9542adebd01e9420bd52f29d0608c4ad7a660390","tid":2499120,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fcf71a35d7a3e9a41e5b5c4288c895b3400a6e40","tid":2499120,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:44:13.000Z","msg":"3.02萬元港幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n應該係買嘢用剩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-21T15:49:13.000Z","msg":"支那確係老屈埋香港啦  <br />\n係港毒分裂分子既賄金 ! <img src=\"/assets/faces/